I want to study social work. My goal is to help children who have been hurt or ignored. I also want to help families who are having problems. I want to learn more about how to be a good social worker. I want to be able to help people, and I want to be good at my job.

I believe in some important values. These values are: help others, respect people, do the right thing, and be good at what I do. These values are important for social workers. They are also important to me.

I have always wanted to help people. But I was not sure what job to do. In high school and college, I saw people running away from their problems. Some people did not use good ways to deal with their problems. Because of what I saw, I decided to study psychology. I got my degree in 2009 from Piedmont College. After I graduated, I was still not sure about my career. One day, a friend introduced me to a 16-year-old boy. He was very nervous. He was visiting because he was being hurt by his parents. The next day, he called the police. I went to talk to his parents. They were being dishonest about what was happening. They said their son was being manipulative. I realized that I wanted to help children like him.

Another important value for social workers is fairness. We say that every person is important, but we do not always act that way. We mourn when someone dies, but we do not want to be different from others. I do not want to be like everyone else. I believe in fairness and I will fight against injustice. In high school and college, I spoke out against unfairness. I wore clothes that showed who I was, I colored my hair in different colors, and I spoke out against racism and unfair treatment. I will continue to fight for what is right.

This paper looks at the biological and sociocultural models of insomnia. The biological model focuses on genetics and health problems. The sociocultural model looks at how the environment affects people.

The biological model examines genetic information and health problems that can cause insomnia. The sociocultural model looks at how people's environments, such as their race, age, and income, affect their sleep.

We will look at some research on insomnia. This research will explain the different parts of the biological and sociocultural models. Then, we will talk about the strengths and weaknesses of each study.

Insomnia is a sleep problem. It can be caused by different things. Sometimes, it is a sleep problem by itself. Other times, it is a problem connected to another mental health issue. There are several kinds of sleep problems. They can be caused by medical problems or by taking certain medicines.

There are two kinds of sleep problems. One kind is called Dyssonmias. The other kind is called Parasomnias. Dyssonmias are problems with falling asleep or staying asleep. Parasomnias are problems with acting out or moving while asleep.

The biological model says that genetics and health problems can cause insomnia. Our brains have special cells that help us sleep. These cells are in the part of the brain called the hypothalamus. These cells contain a substance that helps us sleep. If these cells do not work correctly, we may have trouble sleeping.

One study looked at mice and found that a special receptor in the brain helps us sleep. This receptor is called the GABAB receptor. If this receptor is not working correctly, we may have trouble sleeping. The study found that a medicine can help people sleep by affecting this receptor.

The sociocultural model says that our environment affects our sleep. If we have a family history of insomnia, we may be more likely to have insomnia. If we are under a lot of stress, we may have trouble sleeping.

This study shows that genetics and the environment can affect our sleep. It also shows that we may be able to cure insomnia by using medicine that affects the GABAB receptor.

This paper is about Central Auditory Processing Disorder (CAPD). CAPD is a problem with the brain. It is not a hearing problem. People with CAPD can hear sounds, but their brain has trouble understanding what they hear.

The brain helps us understand what we hear. It separates sounds and helps us know what someone is saying. People with CAPD have trouble with this part of the brain. It is called the central nervous system (CNS).

CAPD was first talked about in the 1950s. Researchers studied children with speech problems. They made tests to help diagnose the problem. In 1954, a team of researchers in Italy started working on these tests. In 1961, another researcher came up with a way to test how the brain works when it hears two sounds at the same time.

CAPD can cause problems with hearing. A person with CAPD may not know where a sound is coming from. They may have trouble hearing two or more sounds. They may not understand speech patterns. They may not know when someone is being serious or not. They may not be able to block out background noise. They may not be able to make sense of what they hear.

To find out if someone has CAPD, doctors use tests. These tests look at how the person hears and responds to sounds. There are many types of tests. Doctors may ask questions or watch how the person behaves. There is no single test that can diagnose CAPD. Tests may include listening to many sounds and then trying to pick out certain words or numbers.

Teachers can help students with CAPD in a regular classroom. They can make sure the student sits in a quiet place. They can ask the student to repeat what they hear. They can break down instructions into simple steps. They can use visual aids to help the student understand.

The play Twelfth Night says that using a fake identity can be helpful in hiding the truth, but it can also cause problems. If you continue to lie, you may forget who you really are. In the play, the main problem with ending a lie is that you may hurt the people around you.

The play talks about a man pretending to be a woman. This is a big problem because it makes us wonder why the character in the play wants to hide who they are. In the play, a woman named Viola pretends to be a man to protect herself. This works, but it also makes her friends and family unhappy.

Viola is very good at pretending to be a man. She is so good that another woman in the play, Olivia, falls in love with her. Viola also has feelings for a man in the play, but she is pretending to be a man so she can't express her true feelings.

The play may be saying that lying can help people see their true feelings. Some characters in the play may have feelings they don't want to admit. They see the person pretending to be someone else and that makes them think about their own feelings. For example, a woman in the play falls in love with a man who is pretending to be a woman. But she quickly falls in love with a real man who looks like the person she fell in love with. This makes us wonder if she really liked the person pretending to be a woman or if she just liked the look of them.

The play is showing us that people may judge others based on how they look. The woman in the play who falls in love with the person pretending to be a woman quickly forgets about them when the real man appears. This makes us think about how people may be quick to judge others based on looks rather than who they really are.

The German colonial rule was very cruel. It killed many people, especially the Ovaherero and Nama in South West Africa. But the German colonial rule was not the same everywhere. The policies and way of ruling were different in different places. The German colonies were very different from each other.

The colonies with educated Africans were in East Africa. The British took over this area in 1919. They found many Africans who could read and write. German education in Kamerun and other colonies was also very good.

But South West Africa was different. The government did not help Africans much with education. Only a few organizations that were not the government helped Africans learn. The government spent more money on schools for Europeans. The government also controlled the schools for Europeans. This made a big difference in South West Africa. Many Africans did not go to school and could not read or write.

Other German colonies had many educated Africans. But in South West Africa, most people were not educated. This was because of many reasons. We will talk about these reasons in this paper. We will also look at how European settlers and the government felt about Africans.

There are many books and studies about education in German colonies. Most of these were written in German a long time ago. Later, people wrote about education in different colonies and how it was the same or different. One person, Cohen, studied education in South West Africa and East Africa. He said that the number of European settlers in South West Africa was a main reason for the difference in education.

South West Africa was a place with a good climate. Many Europeans lived there because it was not too hot. In 1913, 15,000 Europeans lived in South West Africa. This was more than in any other German colony except East Africa.

Heavy metal music is a big group of music styles. It has grown a lot over the past 100 years. Many subgroups of heavy metal have developed. Some of these subgroups have smaller subgroups. This makes it hard to list all kinds of heavy metal music.

Heavy metal music started out a long time ago. But over the years, it has changed a lot. People started to make their own types of heavy metal music. This led to many new kinds of heavy metal. Today, there are many different kinds of heavy metal.

So, what is heavy metal music? Heavy metal music is known for being loud and dark. It often has strong beats and strong guitar sounds. Many people in heavy metal bands are very good at playing their instruments. They put a lot of feeling into their music.

Heavy metal music is also connected to the use of drugs. In the 1970s, many people used drugs to create their music. This led to some strange and unusual sounds. Some people say that the use of drugs helped create the dark and crazy sound that is typical of heavy metal music.

Many heavy metal songs have lyrics that are about dark and sad things. These lyrics reflect the darker side of life. One of the first heavy metal songs was "Helter Skelter." It was written by the Beatles and is about the ups and downs of life. It was a response to a song by the Rolling Stones. The Beatles wanted to show that they could make music that was just as heavy and dark as the Stones.

Henri Rousseau was a famous painter. He painted a picture called The Dream in 1910. This painting shows a woman who is very happy in a dream world. But The Dream is more than just a picture. It shows Rousseau's own dreams and goals as a painter. He wanted to be recognized and liked by other artists and people who love art.

Rousseau had a hard time achieving his goal. He had to decide if he should paint like other artists or be different. He wanted to fit in with the art world, but he also wanted to be himself.

To understand The Dream, we need to know something about Rousseau's life. He was born in a town in northwest France in 1844. His father was a hardware dealer and had a good job. Rousseau grew up without learning art. He worked for the government until he was 40 years old. People called him a customs inspector, but he was really a gabelou.

Rousseau's first wife died when their eight children were young. He was left with a daughter and a lot of sadness. He started painting to feel better and find a new life. Unlike other artists who painted about the poor, Rousseau painted about everyday people like himself.

Rousseau wanted to be accepted by the art world. He was older than many other artists, and they were famous already. But he didn't get recognition until the same time that another artist, Matisse, was becoming famous. They were different because Matisse wanted to paint in a new way, but Rousseau wanted to paint in a way that was accepted by the art world.

We know that many great thinkers believe there is a strong connection between ethics and beauty, between what is true and what is good. I agree with this idea. The poet John Keats said, "Beauty is truth. Truth is beauty. That is all you need to know." We learn many things in life through education and experience, but we also feel that ethics and aesthetics are special. They are not just rules or laws. Our studies of morality and beauty try to explain why something is beautiful or why an action is right. But we cannot fully explain these things. When we talk about a great work of art or literature, we can talk about its details, but we often can't fully explain why it is so good.

For example, we can discuss the details of Leonardo da Vinci's Mona Lisa, but we can't fully describe what makes it beautiful. When we talk about our favorite work of art or literature, we often say things like, "There is just something about it." This "something" is hard to explain. I believe that both art and morality have this quality. As the writer Flannery O'Connor said, "A story is a way to say something that cannot be said in any other way." We can describe the details of a story, but there is something more to it.

I think that ethics and aesthetics are connected because they work in the same way. We experience them at a deep level, but we can't fully explain them. This connection is even stronger with literature. Literature is special because it deals with values. Literature helps us understand what is important in life. The writer McKean said, "What makes literature special is its moral quality. Literature is important to us because of the values we find there."

Germany is a strong country today. It is a united country with a mix of cultures. You can feel this mix in many places in Germany. From München, near the Alps, to Kiel, a city by the Baltic Sea. You can also feel it in Köln, on the river Rhine, and in Dresden, on the Elbe River.

Germany has a unique culture. But it comes from many different places. Many different tribes lived in Germany long ago. The country is called Germania. Scholars and historians do not agree on where the name came from. Some think it came from a group of people called the Tungrians.

A long time ago, a Roman leader named Julius Caesar wrote about the people of Germania. He used the word "Germanus" to describe them. He got this word from the Gauls, a group of people he fought against. Caesar used the word to show the difference between the Gauls and the people he had not yet defeated.

Some people think the word "German" comes from a spear called a "ger". Others think it comes from an old Irish word "garim", which means "to shout". This might mean that the Germans were loud.

A Roman historian named Tacitus wrote about the origins of the Germans. He said that the Germans were an old group of people who did not mix with other groups. They lived in a rough country with bad weather and were not easy to live with. Not many people from Rome wanted to live in Germany.

The Romans would sometimes send armies to Germany to get goods. But they usually went back to Rome. The Germanic tribes lived on the edge of the Roman Empire. They traded with the Romans and served in the Roman army.

I looked down at the toilet in front of me. My mind was empty. I did not think about the toilet or what I was seeing. I just looked. My brain was like a tool that worked by itself. It took in what I was seeing, but did not think about it.

I had always wanted to draw. When I was six years old, I started to think about drawing. Later, I found a book called "The New Drawing on the Right Side of the Brain." It teaches people to draw. One thing it says to do is to put a square around the thing you want to draw. This makes it easier to see.

I could not do that with the toilet in front of me. It was too much. I was amazed. Many artists have their own way of seeing things. Picasso liked blue. Monet liked green. The old masters used all the colors. If I wanted to be a good artist, I had to start by looking at this brown thing in front of me.

My hand moved to the toilet handle. I pulled it down. But the brown thing did not move. I pulled it down again. It still did not move.

I grabbed a mop and stood in front of the toilet. I was not happy. Someone had left a messy present for the toilet cleaners at Rite Aid. I used the mop to try and get the brown thing out of the toilet. I used the toilet paper to make my hand warm and protected. Then I slowly put my hand in the toilet bowl. It was like putting a turkey in the oven for Thanksgiving.

More and more teenagers are dying in car accidents.  Several reasons work together to cause this problem.  One reason is that the young brain is not ready for the dangers of driving.  The young brain is not experienced.  This lack of experience causes many deaths.  It also causes many accidents, such as turning over, speeding, and driving off the road.

Teenagers are also more likely to have accidents when they drive with their friends.  A study in California found that the number of car accidents increases with the age of the passenger.

Some states, including California, have made a rule for teenagers who are learning to drive.  These rules say that teenagers can only drive for a few hours a day and cannot drive with friends who are also teenagers.  But I think these rules are not enough.  The real problem is that young drivers are not good at handling the dangers of driving.

A psychologist named Marvin Zuckerman says that people under 20 years old are not ready to drive.  He has studied how young people like to take risks.  This makes sense.  If we give driver's licenses to young teenagers, many more people will be hurt or killed in car accidents.  In a few years, the number of deaths will be very high.  Many more teenagers will be able to drive soon.

If we want to keep our teenagers safe, we need to make a rule that says no one under 18 can drive a car.  Schools can still teach teenagers how to drive.  But teenagers must wait until they are 18 to get a driver's license.  We can still give teenagers a special permit that allows them to practice driving with an adult.  They must practice for a certain number of hours before they can take a test to get a driver's license.

This is not a new idea.  Many states already have rules like this.  We can make a rule that is the same for all states.  This will help keep our teenagers safe.

I looked at films from the Library of Congress. I chose to watch trick films from 1895 to 1901. There were 15 of these films. They trick the eye with creative editing. My study of these films looked at their artistic side and how they changed over time. 

Most of these films stay in one place and do not move. The camera does not move. The films are long and use many shots to create an illusion. 

One thing trick films have in common is they are shot in a fixed place. The camera does not move to follow people or objects. This style came from theater and magic shows. In these films, people move side to side. They do not move towards or away from the camera. 

Most trick films are long shots or medium shots. They are not close-ups. This is like theater, where the audience sees the whole performance. Actors do not move towards the camera. 

Most trick films are short, usually less than a minute. They are like magic tricks. They do tricks, like making things disappear or change. One trick film shot does not always mean one physical shot. It might be many shots joined together to make an illusion. 

One early trick film is The Execution of Mary, Queen of Scots. At first, it looks like one shot. But if you look closely, you can see when the camera shot of Mary's fake head starts. The whole film looks like one shot to the viewer.

John Taylor of Caroline was a strong supporter of Republican ideas. He was a farmer, but his work and short time in politics made him known for caring about personal freedom and government. He believed that farming was the best way of life, and this idea guided his thoughts on the government. He wanted to protect and support farmers, which influenced his views on power, laws, and the justice system.

John Taylor thought the United States had a great chance to create a perfect system of government. There was no old tradition to follow, so the country's founders could create a system that worked for everyone. He believed in the natural rights of people, which are basic rights that everyone has. He thought that if one person does not have these rights, others will suffer too. These rights should not be controlled by the government.

Taylor believed that in a society, some people might use their strength and cleverness to get what they want. But in a country, this should not be the way things work. To create a good society, the government should understand that people have good and bad qualities. Taylor thought that a government should protect private property, help farmers, and prevent people from getting too much power. He believed that a government like this would work well no matter who was in charge.

Taylor also believed that people are motivated by self-interest, but this is only bad if it means hurting others. He thought a good government should control people's bad qualities and watch out for bad principles that can harm society. A good government would keep people from being cruel to each other.

Taylor wanted the government to limit its power, as stated in the Constitution. He thought a big government was expensive and could be unfair. However, he also believed that following the Constitution too strictly could lead to problems. He thought the Declaration of Independence was more important because it said the United States was a group of independent states, not just one country.

We look at Figure 17. There was a big drop in commuter log entries in the third month of the project. This was not good news. We do not know why this happened. It is possible that the drop in people walking or biking because of winter weather is partly to blame. In New England, people often need to walk or bike less in winter. In December, students and teachers are busy finishing schoolwork and getting grades. They may not have time to fill out the commuter log. This month also starts the holiday season. Many people do not need to go to school for a month. Classes will start again in late January. But we do not understand why people were not filling out the log in February. Maybe people have less energy at the beginning of a project like this. We tried to solve this problem by creating the Carpool Challenge Week. This was a special effort to get people excited about the project again. It worked and we got more log entries in March. So, we need to find a way to keep people interested in the project. We also need to fight against people's love of driving their cars. This is a big problem in our culture. We tried to solve this by offering prizes like gift cards. We gave these out at local restaurants, coffee shops, and stores. We thought this would help people change their behavior. But it would have been interesting to see if bigger prizes would help even more. For example, we could have given away a bike, a hybrid car, or an electric car. This could have helped people be more interested in the project. The prizes we offered did not change during the project. If we had offered bigger prizes in December and January, it might have helped people be more interested.

An ETF, or exchange traded fund, is a security that follows a group of stocks or a commodity.  It is like an index fund but is more flexible and can be bought and sold on an exchange like a stock.  ETFs give you the benefits of many stocks and the ability to buy and sell easily.  They have low costs, but you must pay a commission to buy or sell them.  Many ETFs are available.  Before buying an ETF, it is a good idea to look at its benefits and see if they are real.

We will look at the ETF IHF.  This ETF has ten main stocks that make up 63.58% of all its assets.  We will compare the returns and risks of these ten stocks to the ETF as a whole.  If we use the same amounts of these ten stocks together, we can see how well they represent the ETF.

Our calculations show that these ten stocks could give a 16% higher return than the ETF.  They also have less risk.  But we need to know if these results are real or just a chance.  To do this, we will look at the risk of each stock and see how much it adds to the overall risk of the portfolio.

We will examine the standard deviation of each stock to see if the portfolio of ten stocks is truly less risky than the ETF.

Edgar Allan Poe says "Dream-Land" is one of his best poems. In "Dream-Land," Poe uses the word "Thulé." He got this word from a famous writer named Virgil. Virgil used "Thulé" to describe an island north of Britain. This island was the edge of the known world for the Greeks.

Poe was interested in German writers. One of them is Goethe. Poe liked Goethe's writing. In fact, some people think Poe copied some of Goethe's ideas. A man named Karl J. Arndt wrote a book about this. He said Poe's poem "Politian" is similar to Goethe's poem "Mignon."

Goethe was a well-known writer of a play called "Faust." This play was published in two parts. The first part was released in 1808, and the second part was released in 1832 when Goethe died. Inside "Faust," there is a short poem called "The King of Thulé." This poem is about a king who loses his wife. After she dies, he drinks a lot and cries. He then decides to die too. Before he dies, he gives his money and things to his children. The only thing he keeps is a special cup his wife gave him. He goes to a cliff, throws the cup into the ocean, closes his eyes, and dies. The king in "The King of Thulé" and the king in Poe's "Dream-Land" are very similar. They both have a sad story about loss.

Poe mentions Thulé twice in his writings. He says "ultma Thule" in "The Pit and the Pendulum," but he uses "Thulé" twice in "Dream-Land." "The King of Thule" and "Dream-Land" are like two poems that go together. In "Dream-Land," the speaker says he is in a place called Thulé. He describes Thulé as a dark and lonely place. He sees dead friends and a world without color. This is similar to "The King of Thule" by Goethe. In "The King of Thule," the king is also lonely and has lost his wife. He has lost his will to live.

Goethe was a famous writer that Poe liked. Poe respected another writer named Tennyson. Poe admired Tennyson's work. Poe would have known Goethe's work because of Tennyson. Poe also saw many reproductions of Goethe's writing after it was first published.

In California, a customer who gets hurt after slipping and falling on a spill in a store can ask for extra money from the store. This money is called punitive damages. But to get it, the customer must prove that the store manager acted with mean intention. 

Imagine a customer slipped and fell on applesauce in a store. The store manager knew about the spill twice, but he did not clean it for 30 minutes because he was eating dinner. A judge is not likely to throw out the customer's claim for extra money. The customer must show that the manager knew his actions could cause harm and he did not care. 

There was a problem with spills in the store before. Many customers had slipped and fallen. The manager knew about this. But he did nothing to fix the problem. This is why the customer is asking for extra money. The customer will say that the manager was mean and did not care about the harm he could cause.

A manager at the store found out about the spill twice. He said he was busy eating dinner and did not have time to clean it. But he did not clean it for 30 minutes. The customer slipped and fell and got hurt. Before this, five other customers had slipped and fallen in the store. The customer is suing the store for money to pay for her injury and to punish the store for its actions.

In California, a customer can ask for extra money if the store manager acted with mean intention. The law says this is when the manager knew his actions could cause harm and he did not care. A court decided this in a case where a manager knew his actions could cause harm and he did nothing to stop it.

Four years ago, I took a course in Islam at CBC.  We discussed whether Islam is a hostile religion.  Now this question is more important than ever.  I have seen how the media changed its view of Islam.  After 9/11, the media was against Islam.  Now it is very tolerant.  I think it is interesting that in 2001, a presidential candidate like Barack Obama could come to power.  He has Muslim family members.

I am interested in the story of the Prophet Muhammad.  What I learned about him did not match his biography.  I thought he forced people to become Muslims.  He took over tribes and made them join Islam.  But his biography says he was a humble person who was often misunderstood.  People came to him because they believed in his teachings.

There are many similarities between Muhammad's life and the life of Jesus.  One example is when Muhammad had very little food and made it multiply so that many people could eat.  This kind of writing makes me think the authors wanted Muhammad to look like a humble prophet who did not need to prove anything.  He just lived a truthful life with miracles.  I think this is a problem because it makes Jesus' life and teachings seem less important.

I do not like the way the biography presents stories.  Many of the stories come from people who heard from others.  This makes the stories seem suspicious.  I think the authors wanted to show that people converted to Islam on their own.  But I do not think this is true.

What worries me most is that the biography tries to make Muhammad look like a good and humble person.  But history says he was not like that.  I wonder if Muslims today know the truth about Muhammad's past.

We can see a change in Christian thought since Jesus' time.  People did not follow his teachings after he died.  A new path was chosen.  If we look at history, we can see a pattern.  Christians moved away from what Jesus believed.  Today, we see many people are more open-minded.  They want to know more about the past.  Traditional people will still exist, but they will not be the only ones.  Many Christians will learn more about Jesus' life and teachings.  They will want to know the original ideas of the Christian religion.  It may take time, but the result will be clear:  Christians will go back to the beginning.  They will remove ideas that were added later.  They will go back to what Jesus said.  It will be like a clock moving backward.  Only the true ideas of Jesus will remain.

In the United States and Europe, people will follow Jesus' ideas more closely.  They will worship like he taught.  The church will still be strong, but it will be simpler.  People will follow the same ideas everywhere.  We will see less difference between different Christian groups.  History shows us that this can happen.  Christians were once treated badly by the Roman Empire.  But later the empire became Christian.  Our country went from being against African-American rights to having African-American leaders.  The same thing will happen with Christianity.  People will go back to the source.  They will see that Jesus' words are not always meant to be taken literally.

Looking back in history, we see that Christianity started with Judaism.  The Jewish people had many different groups.  They had Sadducees, Pharisees, Essenes, Zealots, and many common people.  They did not agree on everything.  By the time the Romans took control of Jerusalem in 63 B.C.E., the Jewish people believed in one God.  They believed in the Bible and its teachings.  But they were not the same.  They had different ideas.

The Jungle shows that people are naturally selfish and only care about themselves. They want to make their lives better, but they do not care about others who are less powerful. The book shows this in many ways. The factory owners and managers are an example. They want to make their factories big and strong. They do not care about anyone or anything that gets in their way. They do not care about the pollution that harms people and animals. They also do not care about their workers. They work the workers very hard and pay them little.

The workers have no rights. They can work long hours and then lose their jobs without warning. There were no laws to protect the workers in that time. The factory owners and managers were like slave drivers. They treated the workers very badly and had no sympathy for them. The workers were like slaves and had no way to escape their hard lives. They were very poor and had to live in bad conditions.

The book shows that people are naturally selfish. The factory owners and managers show this. They only care about making money and do not care about others. The workers are helpless and have no rights. They live in difficult conditions and have no way to get better.

Many writers use different ways to make readers feel a certain way about important subjects. 
F. Scott Fitzgerald uses these techniques in his book The Great Gatsby. Sometimes, he pairs a word with another word that do not usually fit together to create a certain feeling. Other times, he gives meaning to a symbol and uses it for the same purpose. 

Fitzgerald uses the last technique with many colors, including gold, green, white, gray, and red. He builds meaning for these colors and then uses it to show readers a feeling about an important thing. 

Fitzgerald creates meaning for white and gray. He thinks white is better and more upper class, and gray is older and faded. He shows this in the beginning of the book by using these colors many times. 

Daisy and Jordan are always wearing white. Everyone wears white at Gatsby's party. Nick wears white clothes, Tom wears a white shirt, and Catherine looks very white. The only time people are not wearing white is when Nick describes Gatsby's party and sees many bright colors. Fitzgerald also uses white and gray to describe ordinary things. 

As Nick goes to work, he goes down a white valley in New York. The names of people at Gatsby's party are gray on Nick's list. Catherine's apartment is like a long white cake. He also describes ordinary people and places as white or gray. Jordan and Daisy have a white childhood, there are gray cars and land in a sad place, an Italian child is gray, and a dog-seller is an old gray man.

After Fitzgerald gives meaning to white and gray, he uses them to show readers that something is not important or is the same. He uses this technique with Daisy first. After a long time, Fitzgerald describes Daisy as a woman in white. Readers start to see Daisy as not a person, but as something Gatsby wants. 

Fitzgerald uses this technique many times with Daisy to show that she is not special. For example, there is a gray fog on Daisy's fur, and she wears a white dress before Tom and Gatsby meet.

San Diego County is a great place for growing food. The climate is good and the sun shines a lot. Farmers grow many things here, including tomatoes, oranges, leafy greens, squash, broccoli, herbs, peaches, lemons, berries, and honey. People want to eat food grown without chemicals, and many organizations in San Diego have long waiting lists. Many farmers also sell organic eggs and milk.

Some farms in the area allow visitors to walk around and see how they grow their food. Farmers can earn money by giving tours and offering hiking and birdwatching. This can also help the environment. The government gives money to farmers who grow food without chemicals, and this can help protect the land and wildlife.

But farming without chemicals can be harder and more expensive. Farmers must work harder and spend more time removing pests and weeds and fertilizing the soil without using chemicals. They can also lose more food than farmers who use chemicals. Small farms are less efficient than big farms because they do not have as much land. They must also spend more time and money on things that help the environment, such as planting special crops and removing invasive plants.

The land I chose is in a place called Potrero, California. It is 160 acres of land with different types of plants and trees. Many species of plants and animals live here, including some that are endangered. The government is making a plan to protect this area and the animals that live here.

People lived on this land for a long time before it was used for farming. It was used to raise cattle and sell wood. Now, I want to show how a farmer could grow food here and protect the environment at the same time.

I found a real farm in the area and used it as an example of what a farmer could do. The farm is in the same climate and has the same types of plants and animals. The farmer can get help from the government and make money by giving tours and selling organic food.

Culture is very important in any negotiation. To understand culture, we must know what it is not and what it means. Culture is not the same everywhere. It is not a single or uniform thing. Making general statements like "all Russians are stubborn" or "all Japanese are accommodating" is not helpful. It is better to learn about a culture and how it will affect the negotiation.

When we meet a new culture, we can compare it to our own culture. We can learn about its history and its problems. Instead of judging or trying to change a culture, we should accept it and work within its rules. This is especially true if we are in a weaker position in the negotiation.

Culture is not just about countries. Companies also have their own culture. In one company, people may work long hours. In another company, people may have a more relaxed schedule. We can see a company's culture in the way employees dress, how they communicate, and who they hire.

Values are very important to understand. They tell us why people behave in certain ways. If saving face or being friendly is important in a culture, a negotiator will not embarrass his company to get what he wants. If a culture values getting a good deal, a negotiator will try to get the best deal he can.

Learning about a culture and its values is important before a negotiation. But it is also important to get to know the other person. This can help make the negotiation more successful.

There is no God, the fool has said in his heart. This idea is from the Christian Bible, in Psalm 14. Thomas Aquinas and St. Anselm both write about God. They have the same idea in mind. We will compare their ideas about God, but first, we need to agree that they are talking about the same kind of God. If we think of a different kind of God, we cannot compare their ideas. We will assume that they believe in the God of the Bible.

Let's look at St. Anselm's idea. He thinks we can know God by looking inside ourselves. We can understand God by thinking about it. This means that we do not need outside proof for God's existence. We can know it is true just by thinking about it. This idea is called faith. We accept things that are true without evidence. This is a Christian idea.

St. Thomas Aquinas has a different idea. He thinks we can know God through reason and evidence. We do not need faith. This is a good idea for teaching others about God. People can learn about God through logic. St. Thomas gives five reasons why God exists. They are cause and effect, change, possibility, order, and perfection. He says that if we know one piece of a puzzle is missing, we can know what it looks like without seeing it.

A long time ago, in the fifth or sixth century BC, a prince was born. He would later be called Buddha. This prince lived a long time ago and left the world to find inner peace. He became a wise teacher, and his teachings made Buddhism. Buddhism is a very old religion - over 2,500 years old. It has changed much since Buddha was alive. We can see this in the country of Sri Lanka, where Theravada Buddhists live. They have a special ceremony every year to cut water. Many people, both monks and people who are not monks, take part in this ceremony. However, Buddha never taught about such a celebration. Theravada Buddhism is different today than it was when Buddha was alive. This is true not just in small ways, but also in its deepest teachings. The Theravada Buddhist community has changed its ideas over time. This happened because of both good and bad things.

There are some important words we will use in this discussion. We will talk about inside and outside forces. An inside force is something that comes from people who believe in Buddhism. An outside force is something that comes from people who do not believe in Buddhism. A bad force is anything that harms the Buddhist community. A good force is anything that does not want to harm or help the Buddhist community, but it may do one or the other anyway.

First, we need to learn about the basic ideas of Theravada Buddhism. Buddhists believe in three things: the Buddha, the Dhamma, and the Sangha. The Dhamma is like a book. It is made up of the Tripitaka, which is three baskets of Buddhist text. The Sutta Pitaka has all the Buddhist talks. The Vinaya Pitaka has rules for how to live. The Abhidhamma Pitaka has ideas about the world and how it works. Some of these ideas are that we do not have a soul, that life is full of suffering, and that everything changes. If we understand these ideas, we can stop suffering. We can also stop being trapped in the cycle of death and rebirth. This cycle is called Sansara. Along with Sansara, we can stop having too much desire, hatred, and confusion. This happens when we become enlightened. The Vinaya Pitaka says how we should live. For people who are not monks, there are five rules: do not kill, do not lie, do not take something that is not yours, do not have sex with someone you should not, and do not take bad substances. For monks, there are many more rules. The most important idea in Buddhism is the four noble truths. The first truth is that life is suffering. The second truth is that having too much of something can cause suffering. The third truth is that suffering can be stopped.

The United States and Mexico had a long-lasting rivalry for 57 years. This rivalry started in 1836 and ended in 1893. The two countries fought a war in 1846-1848, and the United States won many battles. They took control of Texas and the American Southwest. The two countries disagreed on many issues, including religion, culture, and money. Their differences in interest led to many conflicts.

The United States and Mexico are not the only countries with a long rivalry. Countries that share a border often disagree on things. This is true for the United States and Mexico. They are not the only countries with a long rivalry. Cuba is another country that has had problems with the United States.

The United States and Mexico disagreed on religion. This is a common problem for many countries. In the past, the United States was against Catholicism. Mexico is a Catholic country. This made it hard for the two countries to have good relations.

The United States and Mexico also disagreed on who should be in power. This was a problem because of how the English and Spanish treated each other. The United States and Mexico got these feelings of distrust from their former rulers.

There were 17 fights between the United States and Mexico in 57 years. Most of these fights were over land and border problems. Some people from the United States would cross the border and cause trouble. To stop this, both countries used their armies to control their borders.

As time passed, Mexico became weaker, and the United States became stronger. This helped the rivalry end. The United States stopped wanting to take more land from Mexico and instead focused on helping Mexico economically.

Fifteen years ago, I became very sick. I was a nurse. I chose this job because I wanted to feel safe. When I was a child, I did not have a safe home. People told me, "You will always find work. People are always sick."

But I wanted to be a scientist or a journalist. I wanted to learn many things. Even so, I chose nursing. Now I am 61 years old. I have no money. I have been on disability for 15 years. I am still very sick. Every day is hard. I need help from my family and friends. They help me a lot. I am not strong anymore.

My point is that accidents and problems can happen. We can prepare, but we cannot always solve our problems alone. We need help from others.

I think we should not depend too much on the government. The government is not perfect. We should learn to help each other and ask for help. We should not build our own shelters alone.

Some people say that Americans are strong and independent. But our ancestors were strong because they helped each other. They worked together. They shared food and resources. When pioneers traveled across the country, they did not go alone. They worked together.

So, be prepared. I have a disaster kit and food. I have flashlights and candles. But I also know my neighbors. You should know your neighbors too.

Scientists want to know why living things change over time.  They are looking for rules that help explain how these changes happen.  Many years ago, a scientist named D'Arcy Thompson said that it is hard to use math to understand how living things develop.  Today, scientists are still trying.  A team of researchers is using math to study how shells of a type of animal called Prunum grow and change over time.

They are using X-rays to take pictures of the shells.  These pictures help them measure the shape of the shells.  They are then using a computer program to create pictures of what the shells might have looked like in the past or in the future.  This helps them understand how the shells changed over time.

A shell is like a tube that grows in a spiral shape.  It turns around a center point called the columella.  The shell has lines called sutures that divide it into parts.  The last part of the shell is called the body whorl.  The other parts are called the spire.  The tip of the spire is called the apex, and the other end is called the base.  The shell has an opening called the aperture, and the animal comes out of this opening.

There are four ways to look at a shell: from the top (apical), from the bottom (basal), from the front (apertural), and from the back (abapertural).  Usually, people look at the shell from the front.

To count the turns of the shell, you look at it from the top and find the first line that divides the shell.  Then you draw a line and count the turns from there.  Each turn is divided into four parts.

The shell is like a path that the animal follows as it grows.  You can find the path by looking at the center of each turn and the size of the turn.  This path can be shown on a graph and mathematically explained.  Once you have the math, you can change the rules and see how the shell would grow differently.

The number of babies and young children dying in Indonesia has not changed much in the last ten years.  The country is making progress in some areas, such as making sure people have clean water and sanitation.  However, the progress in health care for mothers and children is not fast enough to meet its goals by 2015. 

Many reasons are behind this problem.  We will look at these reasons and see that Indonesia needs to make its health system stronger instead of just focusing on special health programs.

Indonesia has made some improvements.  More births are now attended by trained health workers.  But this number includes traditional workers like midwives who may not have the skills to help in emergency situations.  This means that many mothers are still dying from problems during delivery.  The health system still needs a lot of work.

Fewer children under five are getting medical help for diarrhea.  We do not have complete information about how well new mothers are being taken care of after childbirth.  But it is clear that this area needs more attention.

Fewer women are having cesarean sections than we would expect.  And the number of cesarean sections is very different between cities and rural areas.  This shows that people in cities have better access to healthcare.  The poor have a hard time getting medical help, often because they cannot afford it.

To improve health care for mothers and babies, the next question is: how can we best solve the problem of not having enough medical services?  Should Indonesia create special programs to help specific areas of health care, or should it focus on making its overall health system stronger?  We know that special programs can be helpful.  They have clear goals and can produce quick results.  But there are also some problems with this approach.  For example, when we give too much money to one area of health care, other areas may not get enough money or workers.  This can happen when we give a lot of money to one area and not enough to others.  We also have a problem with many programs working in the same area and not coordinating with each other.  This can make it hard for people to get the services they need.

Two Victorian novels are different from others of their time. They are Oliver Twist and Wuthering Heights. These novels are not like other Victorian novels. They have mystery and strange things that happen. This makes the characters more interesting. It helps us understand their thoughts and feelings.

In Oliver Twist, strange things happen to Oliver. He sees things that are not real. These things show us what he is thinking and feeling. He has a lot of pain and fear.

One time, Oliver was shot. He remembers it like a dream. He does not have control over what happens to him. This makes him feel sad and helpless. He is not sure who is to blame for his problems. This shows that Oliver is not in control of his life.

Oliver is a victim of his circumstances. He has little power to change his life. Old Fagin is a bad influence on him. He makes Oliver feel defeated and helpless.

The story says: "The day passed quickly. There was no day; it was gone as soon as it came. The night was long and quiet, but it did not last long."

I worked with a group of students after school two years ago. I helped them with their schoolwork. I was good at helping them with English and reading. A teacher asked me to work with a boy named Adrian. He was having trouble reading. Some letters were easy for him, but others were hard. He spoke perfect English, but he was not sure about the alphabet. I thought something was strange.

I met Adrian's mother when she came to pick him up. She did not speak much English. We spoke a little Spanish, but it was hard for me. Then I understood the problem. Adrian could read, but he did not know the English alphabet well. I hope he is doing better now.

I tell this story to show that language can be a problem in school. Even if a child speaks good English, reading can still be hard. We all agree that this is a problem. So, what can we do? For Adrian, the answer was simple. He needed help with his alphabet and pronunciation. But for other children who do not speak much English, the answer is more complicated.

We need to try different things. We can use the dual language system. This means teaching children in two languages. We can also have special classes for children who need help with English. But one thing is not enough. We need to use all of these things together.

The dual language system is a good idea. It helps children learn two languages. This can make them smarter and do better in school. Some people are afraid of this idea. They think it is a waste of money and that only some children will benefit. But this is not true. If we use this system for all children, they will all benefit.

So, how do we do this? Do we need all teachers to speak two languages? No, that would be hard. But we can have special helpers who speak two languages. They can work with teachers to help children learn.

Most people learn as children that there is something bigger than they are. We call this something "God." Some people go to Sunday school to learn about God. Others visit the Temple or look inside themselves for answers. Many people accept the ideas about God that their parents teach them. But some people do not believe in God. They think there is no life after death. We choose our own way to think about God. We try to understand ourselves by looking at our own ideas. We want to find meaning in life.

My father liked cardinals. He said so when I asked him. We sat on our porch, listening to the rain. Our house was old, and the tin roof made a loud sound. My father looked out at the rain. He looked sad and worried. He was not eating well, and his clothes were loose. His hair was thinning. I was afraid to talk to him about how I felt. I was afraid it would make things worse. So I hugged him and sat with him in silence.

My father died in December. He was sick for a long time. The doctors gave him medicine to help him feel better, but it did not work. My birthday was five days before he died. I was sad and alone. I thought about God, but I did not want to talk to him. If God was real, I thought, he had stopped listening to me a long time ago.

I did not want to watch my father die. So I did not. I wanted to remember him as he was, not as he was when he was sick. I knew my father better than anyone. He would not have wanted me to be sad. I stayed in my bed for three days, waiting to hear the news. But no one called me.

The Gothic Novel is a mix of old and new ideas. It is like an oxymoron, as Ian Watt says in "The Rise of the Gothic Novel." People have given the Gothic mode many different opinions. Some think it is not deep, while others praise it for creating a feeling of fear and awe. 

The first Gothic Novel, "The Castle of Otranto," was written by Horace Walpole. It used old and new ideas from romances to create a new way to write stories. Walpole took old theatrical ideas and combined them with new things from modern novels. He called it "A Gothic Story." The Gothic genre uses many old ideas from medieval times, such as theater, architecture, and traditions.

At the time of "The Castle of Otranto," the word "gothic" was used to describe many things, people, and time periods. People thought it was old-fashioned and not sophisticated compared to modern society and literature. The combination of old and new things in the Gothic genre is what made it last a long time and seem both old and new to readers.

One important idea in Gothic novels is chivalry. Chivalry is the idea of training a good knight. It is kept and changed in "The Castle of Otranto." Chivalry is important because it represents the ideal of a brave, honorable, and competent knight. Gothic writers, like Walpole, wanted to show that this ideal was missing in their society. They used the chivalric ideas to make the past seem better and to suggest that people could be better. Walpole wrote "The Castle of Otranto" during a time of trouble in politics. He was unhappy with the future and thought that people had lost the good qualities of the past. He showed this in his character, Frederic, who is a prince, has suffered, and is supposed to be dead. He is like a gallant and courteous knight, but also exaggerated, which is a new idea in the Gothic genre.

Supply chain management is the process of moving goods from making raw materials into finished products. This process includes getting a customer's order, making the raw materials into products, and delivering the products to the customer. The idea of supply chain management was first used in 1982 by a business expert named Keith Oliver. He said it is a way to plan, control, and carry out the steps in the supply chain to satisfy customers quickly and efficiently.

There are six important parts of a supply chain: making products, getting raw materials, storing products, finding the right place to make products, moving products, and sharing information. Business managers use these six parts to give the best service to customers.

First, making products is the first step in the supply chain. It is the base of the whole process. When deciding what to make and how to make it, managers need to know what customers want. To find out what customers want, managers look at the market. The market is a good indicator of what customers need.

Once managers know what customers want, they can decide what products to make and how many to make. They must also decide where to make the products and which factory will work best. This decision is based on how many products to make and how good the products will be. The customer's needs and satisfaction are very important.

After deciding where to make the products, managers focus on planning work and taking care of equipment. Making products is a very important step in the supply chain. Every detail is important, and if not done correctly, it can cost a lot of money and time in the long run. For example, companies like Wal-Mart and Target have a plan for every part of their business. They have a plan for how employees should dress and how to receive shipments from trucks. Having a plan helps companies work smoothly and avoid mistakes.

The second important part of supply chain management is getting raw materials. This means making strategic decisions to decide what a factory can do well and what should be done by other companies. A company may have different groups that make different parts of a product. The manager must decide which group is best for each part. Managers may also decide to work with other companies to make parts. This can help create efficiency and save money.

A sign in Burma says Hitler is alive.

Ellen Page, a famous actress, holds a sign on a street corner. The sign says a strange thing: "Hitler is alive." Burma is a country in Southeast Asia. A group of strong men, the military, controls the country. They took power in 1962 in a violent act. In 2007, people in the street began to protest. The protesters were led by Buddhist monks. They wore special red robes. The people's protests were called "The Saffron Revolution." The government agreed to let the monks meet peacefully, but then the violence started. The military attacked the monks and destroyed their homes. Some news reporters were arrested and put in jail. One reporter from Japan was killed in September 2007. The government said 13 people died, but a colonel who left the army said many more people died.

This has happened before. Many governments want to control their people and stop them from protesting. This has been happening since ancient times. Long ago, some Roman leaders said they were gods and had complete control. Some Japanese leaders were thought to be gods. Today, the leader of the United States talks to a man who leads a group of people who do not agree with others.

We have seen many examples of this. In 1989, people in China protested against their government. Many people died. Some said 200-300 died, but others said 2,000-3,000 died. In the 1990s, a group of people in Rwanda killed many others. They were from a different group. Hitler's rule in Germany was another example. He and his men killed many Jewish people.

Duke Ellington's influence on jazz is very big. He was able to create music for a long time, and this helped him to be creative. He made his orchestra sound very good. In many of his compositions, Ellington plays the piano quietly, but as a composer, he is very good at writing music that lets the band members show off their skills. He wrote the framework for the band to play freely, and he also wrote tightly planned pieces that used the special style of each band member to add musical ideas. This made the orchestra sound good together and created new and original music. Ellington knew the sound of each band member and how they fit together, and this helped him to write some of the most creative and wonderful jazz music in history.

The Grove Music dictionary says that Ellington's sound is special because he used the voice as a musical instrument. One good example of this is Creole Love Call. In this song, Ellington used the voice to add sound and color. He did not use lyrics, which made it easy to hear the music. This song also shows how Ellington liked to work with the style of each band member. It is a slow song with a repeated pattern of 12 bars. There are six parts to the song:

1. The voice and reeds talk to each other, with the voice starting smooth and then getting rougher.
2. A trumpet solo that makes the basic melody sound better and adds long, sad notes.
3. A clarinet solo that is very high and has a special piano sound.
4. The whole band repeats the first part, with the brass and reed sections talking to each other.
5. The climax of the song, where the reeds talk to each other in a high voice, and the brass and rhythm sections play a special kind of music.
6. The song goes back to the first part, with the voice and reeds talking to each other again. This time, the voice sounds like a special instrument.

Ellington liked to use the voice to add color to his music, and this is one of the things that makes his music special.

In Hot and Bothered, Ellington uses his skill at planning the music and his ear for sound to create a special sound. He makes a call and response between a trumpet player named Bubber Miley and a singer named Baby Cox. They use the sound of Miley's playing and the singing of Cox to create a rich and good sound. It Don't Mean a Thing (If It Ain't Got That Swing) uses these ideas, too. Ellington uses a trombone player named Joe "Tricky Sam" Nanton to introduce the melody in a special way.

She felt something was missing. This feeling started when she was 14, when she was a teenager. Three years later, when she was 17, she still felt it. She decided she wanted a person, not just a thing. But she did not like any boys. Some boys had tried to attract her, but she was not interested. She wondered why she felt this way. She thought about it for many years. She had many ideas, but none of them seemed right.

Her home was usually a peaceful place. Her parents were kind and calm. They did not argue with each other. They rarely argued with her. They only disagreed about her independence. Her parents were calm, but she was not. She was fun and liked to do things her own way. This made her a happy person.

Today was not a peaceful day. She went from room to room looking for ideas. She heard a loud voice from the kitchen. She ran to the room and saw her mother on the ground. Her mother was hurt and in pain. The daughter ran to her mother and touched her arm. "Mom, what's wrong?" she asked. Her mother said, "Ow, take me to the hospital." The daughter helped her mother to the car and drove her to the hospital.

At the hospital, there were bad smells and a lot of sickness. But the daughter was not worried. She was too busy helping her mother. She called for doctors and they came. They took her mother to a special bed and looked at her. The daughter sat down and waited.

Her mother fell off a stool while trying to get a vase from a high cabinet.

This study looked at food choices and their effect on heart disease and stroke. The study used a special diet called the "Mediterranean Diet." This diet includes a lot of fruits, nuts, whole grains, and fish. It has less animal products and saturated fats. Drinking some alcohol is okay.

Previous studies showed that people who eat this diet are less likely to die from heart disease. Another study showed that this diet helps people lose weight and lower their bad cholesterol levels.

This study followed 74,886 women between 38 and 63 years old. They did not have heart disease or diabetes. The women answered a series of questions about what they ate every year from 1984 to 2004. The researchers looked at the answers to see if the women who ate the Mediterranean Diet were less likely to get heart disease or have a stroke.

The researchers used a special number to measure how well the women ate the Mediterranean Diet. They looked at the number of heart disease and stroke cases over 20 years. They also looked at the number of deaths from heart disease and stroke.

The study found that women who ate a lot of the Mediterranean foods were less likely to get heart disease and stroke. In fact, they were 29% less likely to get heart disease and 29% less likely to have a stroke.

The United States had a big financial problem in 2007. Many people lost their jobs, the housing market fell, and some big companies failed. This problem is still happening today. We need to understand how this problem started and how to stop it. The financial problem was caused by bad decisions made by the government. They made banks and companies make loans to people who could not pay them back. This was a big mistake because the country's financial system was not strong enough. Two companies, Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac, were forced to buy and sell these bad loans. When people could not pay back these loans, the banks did not have enough money. They sold these bad loans to other people, which made the problem worse.

This problem started many years ago, in 1999. The President wanted to win another term in office. He made a rule to make it easier for people to get loans to buy houses. This rule helped create the problem that happened seven years later. In 1999, the New York Times reported, "Fannie Mae wants to help people with low income get loans to buy houses." But the reporter warned, "This could be a problem if the economy gets worse." He was right. The government helped Fannie Mae, but it made a big mistake.

Many things made the economy worse. Banks made new kinds of loans that were not good. They were called adjustable-rate mortgages and mortgage-backed securities. These loans made the economy more connected to the housing market. Many people and companies borrowed too much money to buy houses. They were not ready for a problem in the housing market. When the housing market fell, many people and companies failed.

The five biggest investment banks in the United States had $4.1 trillion in bad loans in 2007. This was 30% of the country's money. Some big banks like Bear Sterns and Lehman Brothers failed. Others like Goldman Sachs and Morgan Stanley had to become regular banks with strict rules. Fannie and Freddie had $5 trillion in bad loans and were taken over by the government in 2008.

Exposition is a part of writing that can be tricky.  It's the place in your story where you explain a lot about the characters and the world they live in. But too much exposition can be boring.

You know, "show, don't tell" is a basic writing rule. But even with that in mind, it's easy to fall into the trap of writing too much exposition. This can happen when you want to tell the reader too much about your characters and their world.

Let's look at an example. Imagine you are reading a story and you are told that the main character met her husband at a certain time and place, and they got married in a big ceremony. But then you are told even more - that he was murdered in front of her. This can take up a lot of space in the story, and it's not very exciting.

A better approach is to show this part of the story instead of just telling it. For example, you could show how much the husband loves his wife through his actions and words. You could also show how much his presence in her life changed her, by showing how she thinks and feels about him. This would make the reader care about him and be sad when he dies.

The key is to add details that make your story come alive. Instead of just saying "They met, they married, he died," you could make the reader feel like they are a part of the story. This will keep them interested and engaged.

As a writer, you need to balance telling the reader what's happening with showing them. It's easy to get carried away with exposition, but it's better to give the reader a taste of the story and let them fill in the rest with their imagination.

I watched two television news programs from Columbus, Ohio. The first one was on NBC 4 this morning. The main story was about a man in Ashley, Ohio who hurt his wife very badly. His name is Shad Hostettler. The police arrested him. The news program showed his picture. He looked very bad. They talked about this story for two minutes because it was still happening. I think they used the right amount of time for this story.

The second story was about a young man named Travis Buyers. He was shot in the Sharon Woods area. He was 18 years old and very sick from his injury. The police were looking for the person who did this, but they did not know who it was. I noticed that this story was short. I think this might be because the man who was shot is black. I have seen this happen many times before. When a white person is hurt or missing, the news spends a lot of time on it. But when a black person is hurt or missing, the news does not talk about it as much.

The next story was about a helicopter that was shot. The police found a hole in it and think it was shot with a .22 caliber rifle. The police are offering a reward for information that can help them catch the person who did this.

The next story was about the weather. It will be hot and rainy on Saturday. The temperature will be in the mid 80s. They wanted to keep us watching, so they made it a short story.

They also talked about a store that was robbed. A black man took money from the store. He was wearing a dark hoodie and was about six feet tall and 150 pounds. They spent a lot of time talking about how black he was.

Another story was about a man named Rene Rodriguez. He was a big dealer of marijuana. He was caught and will be in prison for 25 years. They said he was Hispanic, but I do not think that was important to the story.

There is a strong connection between brothers. This connection is very strong and cannot be broken. Inside this connection are many feelings: love, pride, jealousy, and anger. Brothers know each other very well. They can see themselves in their brother. When a bad situation happens, the true nature of this connection is clear. This connection can bring both good and bad things. When we understand the feelings that come from this connection, we must accept the results of these feelings. When we look at our brother, we see our own self. We see how others do not see us, but how we really are. Our actions and the results of these actions show our true character.

In the story "The Scarlet Ibis", two brothers show this connection and the strong emotions that come with it. The story takes place in a beautiful and vivid place. The two boys go on a difficult journey. Disappointment and pride are very strong in one scene. Only one brother survives. The story shows this connection through the main character, Doodle, and the way he interacts with his brother. The writer also tells us about the feelings of the main character and his view of the world. These feelings affect his actions.

The main character feels one main emotion: pride. He was angry at his brother Doodle from the beginning. He wanted a brother to teach and play with. He wanted someone to go on adventures with. But Doodle was very sick. He could not do the things the main character wanted. The main character was very sad and angry when he realized this. In fact, he even thought about hurting Doodle. But when Doodle smiled at him, he felt love for his brother. This shows that he really did love Doodle.

The human brain is a very complicated and creative system that helps us process information. The way we talk about the brain has changed as technology has improved. At first, people compared the brain to a piece of wax, then to a piece of paper, then to a book, and now to a computer. But these comparisons are not perfect and can lead to misunderstandings.

The brain processes information in a very special way. First, it takes in information from our senses. Our senses are like special tools that help us feel, see, hear, touch, or taste things. The brain takes this information and changes it into signals that it can understand.

The brain uses two ways to process information. One way is to start with small pieces of information and put them together to understand something new. This is like building a puzzle. For example, when you look at a picture of a black box, you start by seeing the colors and the lines. Then, your brain puts these pieces together to understand that you are looking at a box.

The other way is to use information that you already know to help you understand something new. This is like using a map to find your way. If you see a picture of a black box, your brain might use what it already knows about boxes to help you understand what you are looking at.

The brain also has a special filter that decides what information is important and what you should pay attention to. For example, when you look at the grass, your brain does not notice each individual blade. But if someone calls your name, you hear it clearly.

Information in the brain is stored in three kinds of memory: short-term, working, and long-term. Short-term memory stores information for a short time, like 20 seconds. Working memory is like a computer that stores information while it is being used. Long-term memory stores information for a long time.

The brain processes and stores information in different ways. Some scientists study how people remember things, while others study how computers work, or how the brain itself works. One way to understand how the brain works is to think of it like a network of connections. These connections help us understand how we remember things. For example, if you think of a chair, your brain might connect it to other things like a table or wood.

Aldous Huxley writes a book called Brave New World. It is a story about a future world where people value being happy more than anything else. They are taught from a young age to be happy and not to think deeply about anything. The people in this world are not in charge. A group called the World Controller decides what is best for them. Huxley thinks this is a bad system.

He uses ideas from a man named Karl Marx to show how this system is not good. Marx said that when people work for a company, they do not have control over their lives. They work only for a salary. Huxley's book says the same thing. The people in the story do not think about how they are treated. They are happy to buy things and enjoy themselves.

Huxley is also saying that this system makes people not think for themselves. They are controlled by the World Controller. The people in the story are like pawns in a game. They do not have any power. They are only happy to do what they are told.

In the story, there are different classes of people. The classes are like groups. Some people are more powerful than others. But the people in the lower classes do not know they are not in control. They are happy to be like everyone else. Some people are born with more power than others. But they do not use their power to help others.

Huxley is saying that this system is not good. People should be able to think for themselves and make their own choices. They should not be controlled by someone else. In the story, people do not have deep relationships. They do not love each other. They only care about how they look and what they own.

The people in the story are happy to do what they are told. They do not question anything. This is like what Marx said about people who work for a company. They do not have control over their lives. They are only happy to get a paycheck.

Huxley's book is a warning about the dangers of this system. He thinks it is not good for people. We should be able to think for ourselves and make our own choices.

I am a student at University Park. I have been here for two and a half years. It can be hard to get around the campus. My freshman year, I was in a dorm room in East Halls, near the end of campus. I had to walk a long way to get to classes in the Willard building, near the center of campus. This walk could take 25 minutes, especially in bad weather. I talked to an old friend. He said he stopped riding a bike for a few years, but now he rides one again. He said, "Bikes are great. They are the best way to get around." Riding a bike is good for your body. It is also the best way to travel. If you eat breakfast and ride a bike, you can go 30 miles or more. I live off campus now. I decided to buy a bike. It was a good decision. I ride my bike to class every day. I have a class in Thomas building. It is a 25-minute walk from my home. But if I ride my bike, it takes only 5 minutes. The road to Thomas building is not always easy to ride on. But I need my bike. If I didn't have one, I would have to walk. Walking would take an extra 30-40 minutes every day. This is two and a half hours every week. I am too busy to walk. I need my bike to get to class on time.
